
!! # Skolt Saami noun morphology 

!! This file documents the Skolt Saami noun morphology, lexicon by lexicon.
!! cf. Mosnikoff et al 2020: 356
!! the notions of vowels in 9 rows AβÄ™I, and 5 columns
!! |(A)|a|ΟΛ|a Ι|ΟΛ Ι|ΟΛ Ι|
!! |(B)|ΟΒ|ΟΔ|ΟΒ Ι|ΟΔ Ι|ΟΔ Ι|
!! |(C)|u|o|u Ι|o Ι|u Ι|
!! |(D)|o|ΟΞ|o Ι|ΟΞ Ι|ΟΞ Ι|
!! |(E)|i|e|i Ι|e Ι|e Ι|
!! |(F)|uΟΒ|uΟΔ|uΟΒ Ι|ue Ι (<*uΟΔ Ι)| ue Ι|
!! |(G)|uΟΞ|uΟΛ|ue Ι (<*uΟΞ Ι)|uΟΛ Ι/uαΚΙ Ι|uαΚΙ /uΟΛ Ι|
!! |(H)|iΟΒ|eΟΔ|iΟΒ Ι|ie Ι (<*eΟΔ Ι)|ie Ι (<*eΟΔ Ι)|
!! |(I)|iΟΔ|eΟΛ|ie Ι (<*iΟΔ Ι)|eΟΛ Ι/uαΚΙ Ι|eΟΛ Ι/uαΚΙ Ι|

!! F4,F5, G4, G5, H4, H5, I4, I5 are problematic, and for this reason they are not given as in the book,
!! diphthong + XX and YX -> uαΚΙ Ι, iαΚΙ Ι
!! diphthong + XΥàX and YXX -> uΟΛ Ι, eΟΛ Ι
!! column 1 is high; column 2 is low; column 3 is high with soft sign;
!! column 4 represents (vowel + XΥàX and YXX) context found in +V+Ind+Prs+Pl3 (cf. Mosnikoff et al 2020)
!! column 5 is low with monophthongs and analogically low with diphthongs (see Rueter, 2025 )

!! ## Unclassified words

LEXICON N_ !!= * @CODE@ FOR (STILL) UNCLASSIFIED INCOMING NOUNS.
+Sg+Nom: #; ! TODO: all cases

!testing with make  HFST_LEXC_FLAGS=--Werror
!NMN_PIGS;

LEXICON N_SG-NOM-ORPHAN
! For special +Sg+Nom when orphan from paradigm
+Sg+Nom: K ;

LEXICON N_SG-NOM-WITH-CMP
! For allowing compounding even though a word lacks full paradigm
+Sg+Nom: SG-NOM ;

!! IRREGULAR NOUN nijdd
LEXICON N_NIJDD !!= * @CODE@ nijdd:ni
!!! inflection_type="1"
: NMN_NIJDD ;

LEXICON	NMN_NIJDD	!!= * @CODE@ nijdd:ni
!! * Yaml: **N-nijdd**
!! NMN_1Ο²_IJCC
:jdd SG-NOM ;			!!= * @CODE@ nijdd
:jdd%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 	  		!!= * @CODE@ nijddΟΔn, nijddΟΔd
!! strong_geminate, short_vowel, palatalization
:{ ΙΟ‰}jdd%^PAL%>e SG-ILL ;		!!= * @CODE@ ni Ιjdde
!! strong_geminate, long_vowel
:ΟΒΡë SG-ABE/ACC/GEN_PL-NOM ;	!!= * @CODE@ niΟΒΡë
:ΟΒΡë%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;		!!= * @CODE@ niΟΒΡëΟΔst
:ΟΒΡë SG-COM_IN/PL-OBL ;	!!= * @CODE@ niΟΒΡë, niΟΒΡëid, niΟΒΡëid, niΟΒΡëin, niΟΒΡëivui Ιm, niΟΒΡëitaa

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:ΟΒΡë N_MUORYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ niΟΒΡë-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:ΟΒ{ ΙΟ‰}Ρë%^PAL N_MUORYZH-WITH-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ niΟΒ ΙΡë-

:jdd HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN ;
:ΟΒΡë HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN ;
:ΟΒΡë HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_LARGO ;
:ΟΒΡë SG-LOC-PX ;
:ΟΒΡë HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN ;

+Err/GenreLeudd:ΟΒΡëΟΔ SG-ABE/ACC/GEN_PL-NOM ;     !!= * @CODE@ niΟΒΡë Leudd 2018-09-20
+Err/GenreLeudd:ΟΒΡëΟΔ SG-COM_N ; !!= * @CODE@ Leudd 2018-09-20


! Test data:
!!β²§gt-norm: nijdd #
!!β²§ nijdd:  	 nijdd+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ niΟΒΡë: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Gen
!!β²§ niΟΒΡë: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Acc
!!β²§ ni Ιjdde: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Ill
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëΟΔst: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Loc
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëstad: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg1
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëin: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Com
!!β²§ nijddΟΔn: 	 nijdd+N+Ess
!!β²§ nijddΟΔd: 	 nijdd+N+Par
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëtaa: 	 nijdd+N+Sg+Abe
!!β²§ niΟΒΡë:	 nijdd+N+Pl+Nom
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëi: 	 nijdd+N+Pl+Gen
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëid: 	 nijdd+N+Pl+Acc
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëid: 	 nijdd+N+Pl+Ill
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëin: 	 nijdd+N+Pl+Loc
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëivui Ιm:  nijdd+N+Pl+Com
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëitaa: 	 nijdd+N+Pl+Abe
!!β²§ niΟΒΡëΟΔ≈Ψ:      nijdd+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ niΟΒ ΙΡëe:      nijdd+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Gen



!! CLASS 1 HIGH VOWEL, NO PALATALIZATION NOMINALS
LEXICON N_1Ο²_VCC !!= * @CODE@ papp:pa%^1VOW{ ΙΟ‰}pp
!!! inflection_type="1"
!! similar_to: N_PESS
 NMN_1Ο²_VCC ;
LEXICON NMN_1Ο²_VCC
!! pa{a0}{ Ι0}{p0}p
!! V{V0}{ Ι0}{C0}C
!! Sg_Nom:
!! high-vowel=yes
!! monophthong=yes
!! long-vowel=yes
!! palatalization=no
!! consonantism=quant-gem
!! long-consonant=yes

!!! pos="nominal"
!!! syll_count-in-Sg_Nom="1"
!!! stem-ends-in="consonant"
!!! stem_vowel-in-Sg_Loc="ΟΔ"
!!! stem_with_gradation="yes" 
!! 1.1.1.1.1.1. Sg_Nom="short_vowel|geminate" Sg_Gen="long_vowel|geminate" 

! foot: 2syll
! diphthong: no
! vowel_shift: no
! consonant: geminate
! gradation: yes2
! weak_grade: no
! strong_grade:	geminate
! stem_vowel-in-Sg_Loc: ΟΔst
! Sg.Ill: palatalization-AND-e
!! ## 1. WORDS WITH SINGLE-SYLLABLE NOMINATIVE SINGULARS (2009: 167)
!! ## 1.1 Sg.Loc in -ΟΔst (no vowel shift, all raised)
!!  ΟΔ-stems (Sg.Loc, Ess, Par).
!! ## 1.1.1 Sg.Ill vowel	-e
!! ## 1.1.1.1 Has Palatalization
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1] (Palatalization pattern)
!!  Palatalized: Sg.Ill
!!  Not Palatalized: ELSE
!!    Sg.Ill in palatalization and -e
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1 Lacks Specifically Pedagogical Gradation
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1.1 Has Orthographic Gradation
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1.1[] (Monophthong + Consonant Geminate alternation)
!!  Extra strong grade: Sg.Nom, Ess, Par
!!  Extra strong grade: Sg.Ill
!!  Strong grade: Pl.Nom, Sg.Loc, Sg.Com
!! ## FORMS
!! * Yaml: **N-papp**
!! strong_geminate, short_vowel
: SG-NOM ;			!!= * @CODE@ papp
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 	  		!!= * @CODE@ pappΟΔn, pappΟΔd
: A_DER/SAZH_Y ;

!! strong_geminate, short_vowel, palatalization
:%^PAL%>e SG-ILL ;		!!= * @CODE@ pa Ιppe
:%^PAL N2A_LUOQSSI ;		!!= * @CODE@ N¬ΜA: pa Ιppi

!! strong_geminate, long_vowel
:%^V2VV SG-ABE/ACC/GEN_PL-NOM ;	!!= * @CODE@ paapp
:%^V2VV%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;		!!= * @CODE@ paappΟΔst
:%^V2VV SG-COM_IN/PL-OBL ;	!!= * @CODE@ paappi, paappid, paappid, paappin, paappivui Ιm, paappitaa
:%^V2VV A_DER/LAZH ;

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV N_KUUZZYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ paapp-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^PAL N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ paa Ιpp-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^PAL%^CC2CAllegro N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL-ALLEGRO ;
!! papp+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg3
!! pa Ιpstes

HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN ;
:%^V2VV HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN ; !! e.g. 
:%^V2VV HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_LARGO ; !! e.g. +Use/NG+Sg+Loc+PxSg3
:%^CC2CAllegro SG-LOC-PX_ALLEGRO ; !! e.g. +Sg+Loc+PxSg3 pp:p papstes
 HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN ;

LEXICON N_1Ο²_VCC_PL
+Cmp/SgNom: R ;          !!= * @CODE@ papp
:%^V2VV PL-NOM ; !!= * @CODE@ paapp
:%^V2VV PL-OBL ;      !!= * @CODE@ paappi, paappid, paappid, paappin, paappivui Ιm, paappitaa
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ;                  !!= * @CODE@ pappΟΔn, pappΟΔd
: HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN_PL ;
:%^V2VV HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_PL ;
: HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN-ESS ;

! Test data:
!!β²§gt-norm: papp # 
!!β²§ papp:   	 papp+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ paapp: 	 papp+N+Sg+Gen
!!β²§ paapp: 	 papp+N+Sg+Acc
!!β²§ pa Ιppe: 	 papp+N+Sg+Ill
!!β²§ paappΟΔst: 	 papp+N+Sg+Loc
!!β²§ papstan: 	 papp+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg1
!!β²§ paappstan: 	 papp+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg1
!!β²§ paappin: 	 papp+N+Sg+Com
!!β²§ pappΟΔn: 	 papp+N+Ess
!!β²§ pappΟΔd: 	 papp+N+Par
!!β²§ paapptaa: 	 papp+N+Sg+Abe
!!β²§ paapp: 	 papp+N+Pl+Nom
!!β²§ paappi: 	 papp+N+Pl+Gen
!!β²§ paappid: 	 papp+N+Pl+Acc
!!β²§ paappid: 	 papp+N+Pl+Ill
!!β²§ paappin: 	 papp+N+Pl+Loc
!!β²§ paappivui Ιm: papp+N+Pl+Com
!!β²§ paappitaa: 	 papp+N+Pl+Abe
!!β²§ paappΟΔ≈Ψ: 	 papp+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ paa Ιppe: 	 papp+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Gen

LEXICON N_1Ο²_VKK
 NMN_1Ο²_VKK ;
LEXICON NMN_1Ο²_VKK
!! * Yaml: **N-pakk**
!! strong_geminate, short_vowel
: SG-NOM ;			!!= * @CODE@ papp
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 	  		!!= * @CODE@ pappΟΔn, pappΟΔd
: A_DER/SAZH_Y ;

!! strong_geminate, short_vowel, palatalization
:%^PAL%^PALK%>e SG-ILL ;		!!= * @CODE@ pa Ιppe
:%^PAL%^PALK N2A_LUOQSSI ;		!!= * @CODE@ N¬ΜA: pa Ιppi

!! strong_geminate, long_vowel
:%^V2VV SG-ABE/ACC/GEN_PL-NOM ;	!!= * @CODE@ paapp
:%^V2VV%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;		!!= * @CODE@ paappΟΔst
:%^V2VV SG-COM_IN/PL-OBL ;	!!= * @CODE@ paappi, paappid, paappid, paappin, paappivui Ιm, paappitaa
:%^V2VV A_DER/LAZH ;

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV N_KUUZZYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ paapp-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^PAL%^PALK N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ paa Ιpp-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^PAL%^CC2CAllegro%^PALK N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL-ALLEGRO ;
!! papp+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg3
!! pa Ιpstes

HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN ;
:%^V2VV HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN ; !! e.g. 
:%^V2VV HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_LARGO ; !! e.g. +Use/NG+Sg+Loc+PxSg3
:%^CC2CAllegro SG-LOC-PX_ALLEGRO ; !! e.g. +Sg+Loc+PxSg3 pp:p papstes
 HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN ;

LEXICON N_1Ο²_VYKK_errorth !!= * @CODE@
+Err/Orth: N_1Ο²_VYKK ;
LEXICON N_1Ο²_VYKK !!= * @CODE@ algg:a%^1VOW{ ΙΟ‰}lgg
 NMN_1Ο²_VYKK ;
LEXICON NMN_1Ο²_VYKK
!! * Yaml: **N-algg**
!! 
: SG-NOM ;	    				!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrtt
: A_DER/SAZH_Y ;

:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-ABE/ACC/GEN ;		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-NOM ;		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX A_DER/LAZH ;
:%^PAL%^PALK%>e SG-ILL ;		      		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒ Ιrtte
:%^PAL%^PALK N2A_LUOQSSI ;		      	!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒ Ιrtti
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrtΟΔst
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-COM_IN ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrtin
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 		  			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrttΟΔn
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-OBL ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrti

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX N_KUUZZYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^PAL%^YXX2YX%^PALK N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒ Ιrt-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^PAL%^YXX2YX%^PALK N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL-ALLEGRO ;

HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN ;
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN ;
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_LARGO ;
:%^YXX2YX SG-LOC-PX_ALLEGRO ;
: HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN ;


LEXICON N_1Ο²_VYXX !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrtt:pΟΒ%^1VOW{ ΙΟ‰}rtt
!!! inflection_type="1"
 NMN_1Ο²_VYXX ;
LEXICON NMN_1Ο²_VYXX
!! Sg_Nom: vow_mono:vow_short:vow_high:pal_no:cns_xyy
!! similar_to: N_TAALKYS, N_KOONTYR
!!! pos="nominal"
!!! syll_count-in-Sg_Nom="1"
!!! stem-ends-in="consonant"
!!! stem_vowel-in-Sg_Loc="ΟΔ"
!!! stem_with_gradation="yes" 
!! 1.1.1.1.1.1. Sg_Nom="short_vowel|long_cluster" Sg_Gen="long_vowel|short_cluster" 

! foot: 2syll
! diphthong: no
! vowel_shift: no
! consonant: cluster
! gradation: yes2
! weak_grade: short
! strong_grade: long
! stem_vowel-in-Sg_Loc: ΟΔst
! Sg.Ill: palatalization-AND-e
!! ## 1. WORDS WITH SINGLE-SYLLABLE NOMINATIVE SINGULARS (2009: 167)
!! ## 1.1 Sg.Loc in -ΟΔst (no vowel shift, all raised)
!!  ΟΔ-stems (Sg.Loc, Ess, Par).
!! ## 1.1.1 Sg.Ill vowel	-e
!! ## 1.1.1.1 Has Palatalization
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1] (Palatalization pattern)
!!  Palatalized: Sg.Ill
!!  Not Palatalized: ELSE
!!    Sg.Ill in palatalization and -e
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1 Lacks Specifically Pedagogical Gradation
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1.1 Has Orthographic Gradation
!! ## 1.1.1.1[1].1.1[] (Monophthong + Consonant Cluster alternation)
!!  Strong grade: Sg.Nom, Ess, Par
!!  Strong grade: Sg.Ill
!!  Weak grade: Pl.Nom, Sg.Loc, Sg.Com
!! ## FORMS
!! * Yaml: **N-algg**
!! 
: SG-NOM ;	    				!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrtt
: A_DER/SAZH_Y ;

:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-ABE/ACC/GEN ;		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-NOM ;		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX A_DER/LAZH ;
:%^PAL%>e SG-ILL ;		      		!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒ Ιrtte
:%^PAL N2A_LUOQSSI ;		      	!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒ Ιrtti
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrtΟΔst
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-COM_IN ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrtin
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 		  			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrttΟΔn
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-OBL ;			!!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrti

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX N_KUUZZYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^PAL%^YXX2YX N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒ Ιrt-
+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^PAL%^YXX2YX N_KUUZZYZH-WITH-PAL-ALLEGRO ; !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒ Ιrt-

HatY-STEM-PX-RETAIN ;
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN ;
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX HatY-STEM-PX-WEAKEN_LARGO ;
:%^YXX2YX SG-LOC-PX_ALLEGRO ;
: HatY-STEM-PX-STRENGTHEN ;

LEXICON N_1Ο²_VYKK_PL !!= * @CODE@ aal«Ξ:algg
+Cmp/SgNom: R ;                           !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrtt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-NOM ;                !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ;                                  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrttΟΔn
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-OBL ;                        !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrti

LEXICON N_1Ο²_VYXX_PL !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt:pΟΒrtt
+Cmp/SgNom: R ;                           !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrtt
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-NOM ;                !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrt
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ;                                  !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒrttΟΔn
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-OBL ;                        !!= * @CODE@ pΟΒΟΒrti

! Test data:
!!β²§gt-norm: algg # 
!!β²§ algg:    	 algg+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ aal«Ξ:	 algg+N+Sg+Gen
!!β²§ aal«Ξ: 	 algg+N+Sg+Acc
!!β²§ a Ιl«ß«ße: 	 algg+N+Sg+Ill
!!β²§ aal«ΞΟΔst: 	 algg+N+Sg+Loc
!!β²§ al«Ξstan: 	 algg+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg1
!!β²§ aal«Ξstan: 	 algg+N+Sg+Loc+PxSg1
!!β²§ aal«Ξin: 	 algg+N+Sg+Com
!!β²§ alggΟΔn: 	 algg+N+Ess
!!β²§ alggΟΔd: 	 algg+N+Par
!!β²§ al«Ξtaa: 	 algg+N+Sg+Abe
!!β²§ aal«Ξ: 	 algg+N+Pl+Nom
!!β²§ aal«Ξi: 	 algg+N+Pl+Gen
!!β²§ aal«Ξid: 	 algg+N+Pl+Acc
!!β²§ aal«Ξid: 	 algg+N+Pl+Ill
!!β²§ aal«Ξin: 	 algg+N+Pl+Loc
!!β²§ aal«Ξivui Ιm:  algg+N+Pl+Com
!!β²§ aal«Ξitaa: 	 algg+N+Pl+Abe
!!β²§ aal«ΞΟΔ≈Ψ: 	 algg+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Nom
!!β²§ aa Ιlje: 	 algg+N+Der+Der/Dimin+N+Sg+Gen

!!!
LEXICON N_1Ο²_VUKK !!= * @CODE@ joukk:jo%^1VOWu{ ΙΟ‰}kk
 NMN_1Ο²_VUKK ;
LEXICON NMN_1Ο²_VUKK
!! * Yaml: **N-autt**
!! 
: SG-NOM ;	    				!!= * @CODE@ autt
: A_DER/SAZH_Y ;
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-ABE/ACC/GEN ;		!!= * @CODE@ aaut
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX A_DER/LAZH ;
:%^PAL%^PALK%>e SG-ILL ;		      		!!= * @CODE@ au Ιtte
:%^PAL%^PALK N2A_LUOQSSI ;			!!= * @CODE@ au Ιtte
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX%>ΟΔ SG-LOC ;			!!= * @CODE@ aautΟΔst
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX SG-COM_IN ;			!!= * @CODE@ aautin
:%>ΟΔ ESS/PAR ; 		  			!!= * @CODE@ auttΟΔn
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-NOM ;		!!= * @CODE@ aaut
:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX PL-OBL ;			!!= * @CODE@ aauti

+Der+Der/Dimin+N:%^V2VV%^YXX2YX N_KUUZZYZH-WITHOUT-PAL ;  !!= * @CODE@ aaut-
